        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[蔡英文祝贺拜登当选  称期望台美加强友谊]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p>台湾总统蔡英文今早（8日）在推特上恭贺民主党正副总统候选人拜登和哈里斯当选，并期待台美两地共同努力，加强彼此的友谊并为国际社会做出贡献。</p>

<p>蔡英文也在推特上转发了拜登1月恭贺蔡英文成功连任的推文，并说双方在建立关系方面所秉持的价值观是前所未有强健。</p>

<div class="media_embed">
<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" height width>
<p dir="ltr" lang="en">Now it is my turn to extend congratulations to <a href="https://twitter.com/JoeBiden?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@JoeBiden</a> & <a href="https://twitter.com/KamalaHarris?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@KamalaHarris</a> on being elected President & VP-elect. The values on which we have built our relationship could not be stronger. I look fwd to working together to further our friendship, & contributions to int’l society. <a href="https://t.co/xIvit7emjH">https://t.co/xIvit7emjH</a></p>
— 蔡英文 Tsai Ing-wen (@iingwen) <a href="https://twitter.com/iingwen/status/1325228344720289792?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 8, 2020</a>
</blockquote>

</div>

<p>台湾外交部也在推特上代表台湾政府和人民祝贺两人胜选，并说期待与美国在自由、民主与尊重人权等共享价值上，深化双边友好交流关系。</p>
